{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"15fc35e0b9","title":"和江峡轮船员的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"06e55ce685","index":0,"year":1958,"month":3,"day":null,"articleId":"15fc35e0b9"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji39","name":"毛泽东全集第39卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/39-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji39":{"comments":[{"id":"25b605edaa","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"15fc35e0b9","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是1958年3月，毛泽东乘江峡轮去武汉途中，和船员谈话的一部分。"}],"contents":[{"id":"33473b96c6","type":"title","text":"和江峡轮船员的谈话”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"15fc35e0b9"},{"id":"25b605edaa","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东：（对江峡轮三副、女青年石若仪）当你对一件事物还不了解时，往往是害怕的。正如蛇一样，当人们还不了解它，没有掌握它的特性时，感到十分害怕，但是一旦了解了它，掌握了它的特性和弱点，就不再害怕了，而且可以提住它","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"15fc35e0b9"},{"id":"95d30f9d47","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东：（向石若仪）你在船上工作多久","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"15fc35e0b9"},{"id":"1a2662d3df","type":"paragraph","text":"（石若仪说到有四年多了。）","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"15fc35e0b9"},{"id":"0dd0968a14","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东：（问杨大副）你呢？","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"15fc35e0b9"},{"id":"f551375294","type":"paragraph","text":"杨大副：三十多年了。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"15fc35e0b9"},{"id":"6cede1218d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东：（对石若仪）要好好尚他们学习，他们这些老工人是你的好师傅，水上经验都很丰富，许多知识是书本上学不到的","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"15fc35e0b9"},{"id":"b497c72041","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东：有些地方的航道很不好，在三峡修一个大闸，又发电又便利航运，还可以防洪、灌溉··..","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"15fc35e0b9"},{"id":"7998860311","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东：（对江峡轮船长）你的经验是丰富的，要多带徒弟，把技术传给青年人","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"15fc35e0b9"}],"page":{"id":"813fc5483b","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"15fc35e0b9","start":196,"end":196}}}},"__N_SSG":true}